<text top="1455" left="1798" width="403" height="41" font="font3" id="p1_t103" reading_order_no="96" segment_no="8" tag_type="text">USB  can  be  used  for  short- </text>
<text top="1494" left="1759" width="448" height="42" font="font1" id="p1_t104" reading_order_no="97" segment_no="8" tag_type="text">term  diagnostic  systems  that </text>
